msgid "This --upload option is not available in the Free Version"
msgstr "此 --upload 選項在免費版本中不可用"

#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"For files over {size}MB, Relayed P2P in Free version uses unlimited "
"bandwidth tunnel (may be slower but handles any file size), while Device-"
"to-Device transfers remain fast with no restrictions.\n"
"(Relayed P2P is rarely used — only when direct connection fails.)\n"
"\n"
"✨ NO WORRIES — you can still share files **FREELY**!"
msgstr ""
"對於超過 {size}MB 的檔案，免費版本的中繼 P2P "
"使用無限頻寬通道（可能較慢但可處理任何大小的檔案），而裝置對裝置傳輸則不受限制且速度快。\n"
"（中繼 P2P 很少使用 — 僅在直連失敗時使用。）\n"
"\n"
"✨ 別擔心 — 您仍然可以**免費**分享檔案！"

#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"One peer was unable to establish a Device-to-Device P2P connection and "
"fell back to Relayed P2P. However, it was aborted because the Free "
"version only supports files smaller than {size}MB when using Relayed P2P."
"\n"
msgstr ""
"一個對等端無法建立裝置對裝置的 P2P 連線，因此退回到中繼 P2P。但由於免費版本在使用中繼 P2P 時僅支援小於 {size}MB "
"的檔案，因此已中止。\n"

