msgid "Error"
msgstr "錯誤"

msgid ""
"End-to-end encryption protects your files with strong encryption.\n"
"\n"
"Recipients can download using:\n"
"  • Any web browser (recommended)\n"
"  • FastFileLink CLI\n"
"\n"
"Note: Basic tools like curl/wget won't work with encrypted files."
msgstr ""
"端對端加密使用強加密保護您的檔案。\n"
"\n"
"接收者可使用以下方式下載：\n"
"  • 任何網頁瀏覽器（推薦）\n"
"  • 快檔連結 CLI\n"
"\n"
"注意：curl/wget 等基本工具無法處理加密檔案。"

msgid "End-to-End Encryption"
msgstr "端對端加密"

msgid ""
"Error reporting helps improve FastFileLink by sending crash reports and "
"errors.\n"
"\n"
"What is sent:\n"
"  • Error messages and stack traces\n"
"  • Application version\n"
"\n"
"What is NOT sent:\n"
"  • Your files or file contents\n"
"  • Personal information\n"
"\n"
"You can disable this anytime in Preferences."
msgstr ""
"錯誤回報透過傳送當機報告和錯誤來協助改善快檔連結。\n"
"\n"
"會傳送的內容：\n"
"  • 錯誤訊息和堆疊追蹤\n"
"  • 應用程式版本\n"
"\n"
"不會傳送的內容：\n"
"  • 您的檔案或檔案內容\n"
"  • 個人資訊\n"
"\n"
"您可以隨時在偏好設定中停用此功能。"

msgid "Error Reporting"
msgstr "錯誤回報"

msgid ""
"Error reporting has been disabled.\n"
"\n"
