msgstr ""
"錯誤回報已停用。\n"
"\n"
"此變更將在您重新啟動快檔連結後生效。"

msgid "Error Reporting Disabled"
msgstr "錯誤回報已停用"

msgid "🔍 Detecting Tor connection, please wait..."
msgstr "🔍 正在偵測 Tor 連線，請稍候..."

msgid ""
"⚠️ Tor not detected!\n"
"\n"
"To use Tor privacy mode, you need to:\n"
"  1. Install and start Tor Browser (https://www.torproject.org/)\n"
"     OR install Tor service\n"
"  2. Keep Tor running in the background\n"
"\n"
"Tor Browser typically runs on port 9150\n"
"Tor service typically runs on port 9050\n"
"\n"
"After starting Tor, try enabling this option again."
msgstr ""
"⚠️ 未偵測到 Tor！\n"
"\n"
"要使用 Tor 隱私模式，您需要：\n"
"  1. 安裝並啟動 Tor Browser (https://www.torproject.org/)\n"
"     或安裝 Tor 服務\n"
"  2. 保持 Tor 在背景執行\n"
"\n"
"Tor Browser 通常執行在連接埠 9150\n"
"Tor 服務通常執行在連接埠 9050\n"
"\n"
"啟動 Tor 後，請重新啟用此選項。"

msgid "Tor Not Detected"
msgstr "未偵測到 Tor"

#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"🧅 Tor Privacy Mode Enabled\n"
"\n"
"This mode enhances your privacy by:\n"
"  • Routing all connections through Tor network\n"
"  • Completely disabling WebRTC (server-side enforcement)\n"
"  • Hiding your IP address from recipients\n"
"  • Forcing all transfers to use HTTP-over-Tor\n"
"  • End-to-end encryption (E2EE) enabled automatically\n"
"  • Error reporting disabled for better privacy\n"
"\n"
"⚠️ Important Notes:\n"
"  • Tor must remain running while sharing files\n"
"  • File transfers may be slower through Tor\n"
"  • E2EE is enabled: curl/wget and tools without decryption cannot "
"download\n"
"    (You can disable E2EE in Preferences if needed)\n"
"\n"
"💡 Recommendation:\n"
"  Consider enabling password protection in Preferences\n"
"  for additional access control.\n"
"\n"
"Detected proxy: {proxy}"
msgstr ""
"🧅 已啟用 Tor 隱私模式\n"
"\n"
"此模式透過以下方式增強您的隱私：\n"
"  • 透過 Tor 網路路由所有連線\n"
"  • 完全停用 WebRTC（伺服器端強制執行）\n"
"  • 向接收者隱藏您的 IP 位址\n"
"  • 強制所有傳輸使用 HTTP-over-Tor\n"
"  • 自動啟用端對端加密 (E2EE)\n"
"  • 停用錯誤回報以獲得更好的隱私\n"
"\n"
"⚠️ 重要注意事項：\n"
"  • 分享檔案時 Tor 必須保持執行\n"
"  • 透過 Tor 的檔案傳輸可能較慢\n"
"  • E2EE 已啟用：curl/wget 和無解密工具的程式無法下載\n"
"    （如需要，您可以在偏好設定中停用 E2EE）\n"
"\n"
"💡 建議：\n"
"  考慮在偏好設定中啟用密碼保護\n"
"  以增加額外的存取控制。\n"
"\n"
"偵測到的代理：{proxy}"

msgid "Tor Privacy Mode"
msgstr "Tor 隱私模式"

msgid ""
